QUESTION :1

Exp4 : DML COMMAND- UPDATE

Update the price of a particular product.

Query:

mysql> update product set price='300' where pid=104;  //MENTION THE PRODUCT NAME LIKE 'PEN'
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.04 sec)
Rows matched: 1  Changed: 1  Warnings: 0

mysql> select * from product;
+-----+--------+--------+
| pid | pname  | price  |
+-----+--------+--------+
| 101 | book   |  55.00 |
| 102 | pen    |  15.00 |
| 103 | bag    | 500.00 |
| 104 | box    | 300.00 |
| 105 | sheo   | 750.00 |
| 106 | pencil |  10.00 |
+-----+--------+--------+
6 rows in set (0.00 sec)


