QUESTION :3


Update all prices with 2% of its original price.

Query:

mysql> update product set price=price+(0.02*100);
Query OK, 6 rows affected (0.04 sec)

mysql> select * from product; 

+-----+--------+--------+
| pid | pname  | price  |
+-----+--------+--------+
| 101 | book   |  57.00 |
| 102 | pen    |  17.00 |
| 103 | bag    | 502.00 |
| 104 | box    | 302.00 |
| 105 | sheo   | 752.00 |
| 106 | pencil |  12.00 |
+-----+--------+--------+
6 rows in set (0.01 sec)

